From: zou cao <cao.zou@windriver.com>
Date: Thu, 27 Apr 2017 10:11:51 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] bcmdhd: fix compile issue if build CFG80211 subsystem as
 module

BCMDHD needs to be tristate for the correct dependency
of wireless core subsystem.
it will fixe compile issue when wireless core subsystem is buildin
module.

Signed-off-by: zou cao <cao.zou@windriver.com>
---
 drivers/net/wireless/bcmdhd/Kconfig |    1 +
 1 files changed, 1 insertions(+), 0 deletions(-)

diff --git a/drivers/net/wireless/bcmdhd/Kconfig b/drivers/net/wireless/bcmdhd/Kconfig
index e5bc667..3a8989b 100644
--- a/drivers/net/wireless/bcmdhd/Kconfig
+++ b/drivers/net/wireless/bcmdhd/Kconfig
@@ -1,5 +1,6 @@
 config BCMDHD
 	tristate "Broadcom FullMAC wireless cards support"
+	depends on CFG80211
 	---help---
 	  This module adds support for wireless adapters based on
 	  Broadcom FullMAC chipset.
